{"tid":907033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港拎埋澳門黎管會唔會係新出路？","createTime":"2018-11-18T12:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T18:58:21.000Z","uid":21222,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e89411a8f42a3eaa491f09a39df7649c6070eeec","tid":907033,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:58:59.000Z","msg":"香港澳門取消關口，交通應該快好多兩邊返工可能同屯門出港島差唔多。澳門主力旅遊居住香港對下運輸經濟。你幾千億起個濕鳩人工島不如同澳門聯手拎黎發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 帶起澳門去到另一層次。到時香港分5區 新界 九龍 香港 氹仔 澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5335d8d8fac26a795fb616a6c0b891df4d1be2","tid":907033,"uid":36238,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"與其諗埋啲不切實際既野<br />\n不如認認真真熄連登<br />\n揸起本書裝備自己啦"},{"pid":"bba2dd53b6d7fec3337b5cea00174eb76a425ef2","tid":907033,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:07:58.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"5940838e1673c28b619a99d73325125ee0685959","tid":907033,"uid":29606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a78d5d8b2856ca23d8192c0970773ae7d3cfcf61","tid":907033,"uid":96743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:38:29.000Z","msg":"笑左<br />\nD澳門人年年派錢 年年加福利 要比你拎黎管？<br />\n你邊撚個咁大口氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港做到年年每人派2萬維穩費先好講野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7622ddfb56743d65c75cfa7716e8d0e4388308","tid":907033,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:55:06.000Z","msg":"2047 2049管治權都要比返大陸，但大陸識計數都知無左香港既獨特性，反而係更大損失。但2047香港唔交2049澳門又點會咁順。到時會唔會係香港體系為主咁整合澳門變新香港黎發展會更長遠？"},{"pid":"79d76